playstore_details.description:
If you want to lose weight, have a flat belly and a perfect body, use our 7 Minute Workout, which will help you tone your abs, with video explanations for each move.

7 Minute Workout will be the suitable software for ordinary people to exercise! You can exercise anytime, anywhere, it only takes 7 minutes! You can use it to exercise your major muscles and keep fit safely, effectively and efficiently. Try the 7 Minute Workout App to make you healthier!

· Exercise anytime, anywhere, no equipment required

· Daily exercise challenges help you develop good exercise habits

· Compete with friends to gain more encouragement and support

· Earn achievements as you level up from novice to athlete level

· Personal workouts tailored to individual needs and preferences

· 3D character demonstration makes it easier to master the essentials of actions

You only need to spend 7 minutes every day, and then you can regulate your body and strengthen your body.

Ensure that these permissions are required by the application.

android.permission.POST_NOTIFICATIONS (dangerous): allows an app to post notifications. - Allows an app to post notifications

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW (dangerous): display system-level alerts - Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS (dangerous): act as an account authenticator - Allows an application to use the account authenticator capabilities of the Account Manager, including creating accounts as well as obtaining and setting their passwords.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS (dangerous): list accounts - Allows access to the list of accounts in the Accounts Service.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE (dangerous): read/modify/delete external storage contents - Allows an application to write to external storage.

android.permission.ACTIVITY_RECOGNITION (dangerous): allow application to recognize physical activity - Allows an application to recognize physical activity.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE (dangerous): read external storage contents - Allows an application to read from external storage.
